2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper involves fusing gyroscope and camera data for estimating camera parameters and pose, which is relevant to robotics. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses an extended Kalman filter for online estimation, which is a common machine learning technique. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with video stabilization, which is a multimedia application. 
5. cs.SD (Sound) is unlikely as the paper does not involve any sound-related research.
